Bug ID:017
Title: 17.Change password to current password
Description: You can change your password to your current password.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on your account in the navbar.
Step 4: Click on the Password row to go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/Identity/Account/Manage/ChangePassword).
Step 5: Fill all the fields with your current password.
Step 6: Press the Update password button.
Step 7: Affirm you get the "Your password has been changed." message.

Expected Result:
When you try to change your password to your current password the system should say that your current and new password are the same .
Actual Result:
You can fill all the fields with your current password and after pressing Update password you get the confirmation message that you have changed your password.

Severity:
Medium  

Priority:
Medium

Additional Information:
-

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
